data.description: Custom built colonial in  South Wales Community    Over 5000 finished sq ft on  1+ acre lot backs to trees and open space with oversized 3 car garage, offering a perfect blend of luxury and comfort.  Features  5 spacious bedrooms, 3.5 baths, and exquisite detailing with detailed moldings throughout. The heart of the home is a captivating 2-story family room with a cozy gas fireplace—a perfect spot for gatherings and relaxation  Open to the gourmet kitchen, that  features a generous granite island, breakfast bar, and an amazing light filled breakfast room  framed by walls of windows.  The main level also  includes a  private office with glass doors, ideal for working from home, beautiful hardwood floors , a  two story foyer, formal living and dining room and  a spacious laundry room.  The hardwood stairway leads to a  tranquil owner's suite with a tray ceiling, 2 walk-in closets, and a spa-like ensuite bath. Three additional bedrooms and a guest bath complete the upper level.  Entertainment awaits in the finished basement, offering a sprawling rec room, a custom  fitness room, media area, a spacious 5th bedroom, and a 3rd full bath. Outside, unwind on the Trex deck overlooking your private oasis, surrounded by trees and open space.  The 3 car garage allows plenty of parking space and includes an electric charger.   Move in ready!
